Story Line The young filmmaker Timothy Sandy (Jonathan Welsh) is sent out to investigate 'adult' businesses with his photographer Ralph (Jim Carrey). Much nudity and fun and games ensue.

Timothy Sandy (Jonathan Welsh) is a young, filmmaker with a screenplay. His script tells the heart warming, sensitive story of an orphan and his German Shepherd in search of a family.
